        }
      },
      {
        "heading": "The African Rock Python",
        "content": "<h3>Scientific Name: <em>Python sebae</em></h3><p>One of the largest snake species in the world, the African Rock Python can be found in a variety of habitats across Nigeria, from savannas to forests. Despite its size and power, this python faces threats from habitat destruction and hunting.</p>",
        "image": {
          "source": "https://www.placeholderimage.online/placeholder/800/600/f3f4f6/1f2937?font=Lato.svg/african-rock-python.jpg",
